<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Senderista Packing List</title>

<style>

:root{
--bg:#0b0f19;
--card:#12182a;
--text:#ffffff;
--muted:#9aa3b2;
--accent:#3ecf8e;
}

*{
box-sizing:border-box;
margin:0;
padding:0;
}

body{
font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Segoe UI,Roboto,Helvetica,Arial;
background:var(--bg);
color:var(--text);
line-height:1.6;
}

.container{
max-width:900px;
margin:auto;
padding:40px 20px;
}

header{
text-align:center;
margin-bottom:40px;
}

header h1{
font-size:40px;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

header p{
color:var(--muted);
}

.card{
background:var(--card);
padding:30px;
border-radius:14px;
margin-bottom:30px;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
}

.card h2{
margin-bottom:15px;
color:var(--accent);
}

.card ul{
padding-left:20px;
}

.card li{
margin-bottom:8px;
}

.image{
margin:25px 0;
text-align:center;
}

.image img{
max-width:100%;
border-radius:10px;
}

.footer{
text-align:center;
color:var(--muted);
padding:40px 0;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<header>
<h1>WHAT TO PACK?</h1>
<p>Follow the Senderista Packing List</p>
</header>

<div class="image">
<img src="images/img_0.png">
</div>

<div class="card">

<h2>1. Backpack</h2>

<ul>
<li>Your backpack should have a capacity of approximately 45 liters.</li>
<li>The total weight of the backpack should be approximately 14kg (31 lbs).</li>
<li>Bring a waterproof cover for the backpack.</li>
<li>Your backpack is individual.</li>
<li>Store documents in ziplock bags to keep them dry.</li>
</ul>

</div>

<div class="image">
<img src="images/img_1.png">
</div>

<div class="card">

<h2>2. Documents</h2>

<ul>
<li>Copy of identification with photo</li>
<li>$20 in cash</li>
<li>Passport (for foreigners)</li>
<li>Health insurance card (if available)</li>
<li>Signed liability waiver</li>
</ul>

</div>

<div class="image">
<img src="images/img_2.png">
</div>

<div class="card">

<h2>3. Clothes</h2>

<ul>
<li>Pants for hiking or sports activities (no jeans)</li>
<li>Sports shorts / swim shorts</li>
<li>Short and long sleeve t-shirts</li>
<li>Cap or hat</li>
<li>Underwear</li>
<li>Jacket for cold weather</li>
</ul>

</div>

<div class="image">
<img src="images/img_3.png">
</div>

<div class="card">

<h2>4. Personal Items</h2>

<ul>
<li>Toothbrush and toothpaste</li>
<li>Soap</li>
<li>Deodorant</li>
<li>Small towel</li>
<li>Flashlight or headlamp</li>
</ul>

</div>

<div class="image">
<img src="images/img_4.png">
</div>

<div class="card">

<h2>5. Important Notes</h2>

<ul>
<li>Prepare your backpack carefully.</li>
<li>Do not bring unnecessary items.</li>
<li>Weight distribution is important.</li>
<li>Respect the instructions of the organization.</li>
</ul>

</div>

<div class="footer">
Senderista Packing List • Eagle Path 2026
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
